## 🎯 How to Use

### 1. First Visit (No Account)
```
1. Navigate to: http://localhost:4200
2. You'll be redirected to Login page
3. See animated IoT telemetry widgets in background
4. Click "Register" link
```

### 2. Create First User (Becomes Admin)
```
1. On registration page: http://localhost:4200/register
2. Fill in:
   - Username: admin (or your choice)
   - Email: admin@example.com
   - Password: admin123 (min 6 characters)
   - Confirm Password: admin123
3. Click "Register"
4. You'll see: "You will become an Admin!" message
5. After registration, redirected to Telemetry page
```

### 3. Login
```
1. Navigate to: http://localhost:4200/login
2. Enter credentials
3. See live animated telemetry widgets:
   - Temperature (18-28°C)
   - Humidity (45-85%)
   - Pressure (995-1025 kPa)
   - Real-time data stream
4. Click "Login"
5. Redirected to Dashboard
```

### 4. View Telemetry Data
```
After login, you can:
- View all telemetry data from devices
- See temperature, humidity, and pressure readings
- Filter by device
- View real-time updates
```

